e I'm living in reality as well.<br>: - Jason<p>Dear Jason,<p>I believe that it is possible in our lifetime that you will get the proof you need that there is indeed a spiritual realm to this world.  Unfortunately, the next person to come to earth performing signs and wonders will be the AntiChrist.  Those with very strong anti-christian feelings will probably follow right along when our persecution begins.  Perhaps if it does occur, you'll remember that I told you this.<p>When you turn a key in a lock and it opens the door, you must assume you have selected the right one.  I have tested the teachings of the Bible and found them to be true in every situation.  My relationships and my general well being really hum along when I keep my nose in the scriptures.  When I get lazy and forget to read and pray, the next thing I know, everything is getting screwed up again.  Whether there is a God or not, there is no denying that living by the teachings found in His word are highly beneficial.<br>I'm not perfect by any stretch of the imagination, but I'm a much better and happier person than I used to be.  I was a mess, and I have no problem with giving the credit to the Lord for reaching in and pulling me out of the muck.<br>If you have any part of scripture that you would like to debate that doesn't require me to have a knowledge of geology, I'd LOVE to give you my views.<p><br>
