Posted by <a href="mailto:mtgerety@ix.netcom.com">Grasshopper</a> on January 01, 1997 at 11:22:41:<p>
In Reply to: <a href="585.html">Unlikely Existence of God</a> posted by Amanda on December 26, 1996 at 18:46:35:<p>
There is absolutely no reason to believe in God, obviously for the lack of proof.  However<br>I find it equally foolish to rule out the existence of God...There<br>is no absolute proof so it is better to not to believe one way or the <br>other--both are equally ridiculous.<p>
