: Furthrmore my wife worked in a regiter office-births/deaths/marriages etc
: and someone there beleived she could comunicate with dead peoples pets.

: Its a strange world we live in but people make it even more strange.

: I must say I am lad I came across this site.there is it seems still hope! 
: : 
: regards steve Jarvis

: 
: ps hope ypou got this message

</textarea>
