: : I've just started following this debate, but I wanted to make sure 
: : that you knew, Lynn, that Jason and Amanda aren't the only ones who
: : want you to feel welcome here.  I admire your courage in debating such
: : emotional topics with people who so strongly disagree with you.  I 
: : also want to commend Amanda for her apology.  That took a lot of guts,
: : and showed a lot of heart!

: 
: I think it did, too.

</textarea>
