: : I'm going to miss Sagan, like Asimov he could explain everything
: : so well, with wonder and humor.

: Yes, I read the Selfish Gene in University and have always meant to pick up the Blind Watchmaker. For a moment while I was reading your comments I thought of Stephen Hawkings but I don't much care for his writing - it's a bit dry and choppy.

